CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782645504
OL,3,CNew technique being used to treat
OL,4,Cspinal injuries
OL,6,FSpinal injury can severely affect
OL,7,Fmobility and movement.
OL,9,FNow a ground-breaking technique is
OL,10,Fbeing used in Sussex to improve limb
OL,11,Ffunction.
OL,13,FIt involves sending small electrical
OL,14,Fwaves through the skin on the neck,
OL,15,Fwhile carrying out exercises.
OL,17,FSpinal stimulation therapy, as it's
OL,18,Fknown, has been developed by a
OL,19,Fcharitable trust in Crawley
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
