FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782645504
OL,3,CNew technique being used to treat
OL,4,Cspinal injuries
OL,6,FPeter Brown has made remarkable
OL,7,Fprogress after being told by doctors
OL,8,Fhe would paralysed from the shoulders
OL,9,Fdown two years ago.
OL,11,FIt followed complications during
OL,12,Fspinal cord surgery.
OL,14,FMr Brown said: " I started to get
OL,15,Fmovement back in my right hand, my
OL,16,Fright side first, but I can't feel any
OL,17,Fsensation through my right side.
OL,19,F" But I can feel some sensation for my
OL,20,Fleft.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782645504
OL,3,CNew technique being used to treat
OL,4,Cspinal injuries
OL,6,F"But I have less movement, so I don't
OL,7,Fknow what my leg is doing in space or
OL,8,Fout moves.
OL,10,F"And, previously, I didn't have much
OL,11,Fmovement through my left arm or hand."
OL,13,FThe air conditioning engineer was put
OL,14,Fon an intensive therapy programme.
OL,16,FThat has now been followed up with a
OL,17,Fnew technique called ARC Ex, where
OL,18,Felectrodes are placed on the neck to
OL,19,Fstimulate the spinal cord.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782645504
OL,3,CNew technique being used to treat
OL,4,Cspinal injuries
OL,6,FThis is combined with upper body
OL,7,Fexercises, including those involving
OL,8,Fhands.
OL,10,FPeter Brown added: "I can actually
OL,11,Fhold, a jam jar and undo the lid, I
OL,12,Fuse the coffee pots as an example.
OL,14,F"Before I couldn't hold them and undo
OL,15,Fthem, but now I can do that.
OL,17,F"And it seems really trivial, rather
OL,18,Fthan have to use my teeth for me and I
OL,19,Fcan use both my hands to undo it,
OL,20,Fwhich I couldn't do before."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
