OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782645504
OL,3,CNew technique being used to treat
OL,4,Cspinal injuries
OL,6,FThe non-surgical technique has been
OL,7,Fdeveloped by the charitable trust
OL,8,FNeurokinex in Crawley.
OL,10,FPeople are referred here for an 8 week
OL,11,Fprogramme by their spinal unit or
OL,12,Fconsultant but at the moment the
OL,13,Ftreatment is only available privately.
OL,15,FClinical lead physiotherapist
OL,16,FCatharinah Carvhalo said: " It needs
OL,17,Fto be paired with activities.
OL,19,F"That only happens if we target
OL,20,Factivities in a meaningful way for the
OL,21,Fperson.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782645504
OL,3,CNew technique being used to treat
OL,4,Cspinal injuries
OL,6,F"Picking a book up, being it reaching
OL,7,Fto a cabinet.
OL,9,F"So all the activities that we do
OL,10,Fwhilst the stimulation is on need to
OL,11,Fbe meaningful and very repetitive"
OL,13,FLuca Bukenberger, who's 22, was
OL,14,Fparalysed in a diving accident on
OL,15,Fholiday in Malaysia.
OL,17,FHe has travelled from Germany to
OL,18,FSussex after crowdfunding for therapy.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782645504
OL,3,CNew technique being used to treat
OL,4,Cspinal injuries
OL,6,FHe said: "After my accident happened,
OL,7,FI could barely move anything below the
OL,8,Flevel of my own neck.
OL,10,F"So currently, I'm very happy with the
OL,11,Fprogress, I could regain some
OL,12,Ffunctions below the level, regain some
OL,13,Findependence"
OL,15,FSo far, twenty five people have been
OL,16,Fthrough or are going through this
OL,17,Fspecific type of therapy.
OL,19,FAnd the early indications and results
OL,20,Fseem to be encouraging.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
