OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782645504
OL,3,CNew technique being used to treat
OL,4,Cspinal injuries
OL,6,FNeuro-rehabilitation specialist
OL,7,FMirilla Cameron said: "It's not a one
OL,8,Fsize fits all.
OL,10,F" No spinal cord injury is different.
OL,12,F"Every single person, even if they
OL,13,Fhave the same injury on paper, will
OL,14,Fpresent differently with different
OL,15,Fgoals and different needs.
OL,17,F"And the thing with ARC Ex is you can
OL,18,Fstem directly over the spinal cord
OL,19,Fabove and below that level of injury,
OL,20,Fbut then tailor the tasks to what it
OL,21,Fis that they need to work on."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
