PN,38209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782645504
OL,3,CNew technique being used to treat
OL,4,Cspinal injuries
OL,6,FARC-EX devices have been developed
OL,7,Fafter almost a decade of collaboration
OL,8,Fwith academic institutions, clinical
OL,9,Fgroups and industry experts.
OL,11,FIf successful, this type of approved
OL,12,Ftreatment could one day become more
OL,13,Fwidely available, including on the NHS.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/9
